Package com.iontrading.mkv.events.onbehalfof

Interface MkvOnBehalfOfAuthenticationWithTokenResponseEvent

  • @Keep
@KeepPublicClassMemberNames
public interface MkvOnBehalfOfAuthenticationWithTokenResponseEvent
    Listener used to receive the result of the authentication phase of on-behalf-of registration request performed with token. Note: this interface is not meant to be implemented by application code.

      • getOriginalAuthMethodType

        Optional<String> getOriginalAuthMethodType()
        If the LongTermAuthentication token has been used, this type represents the type of the service that authenticated the user the first time.

        Possible values are: password or token.

        This value is available when Daemon 160p3 or higher is used; otherwise an empty optional is returned.

        Returns:
        the type of the service that authenticated the user the first time.

      • getOriginalServiceId

        Optional<String> getOriginalServiceId()
        Return the service id used to authenticate the user.
        If the LongTermAuthentication token has been used, this service represents the original service id that authenticated the user the first time.

        This value is available when Daemon 121 or higher is used; otherwise an empty optional is returned.

        Returns:
        the service id used to authenticate the user.

      • getExternalUserId

        The user identifier in the external system.
